{"tid":352700,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做左一年半Partyroom，你問我盡答","createTime":"2017-08-09T03:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T11:42:17.000Z","uid":5064,"like":17,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"29d51554e0fa5a4fd1759d377d6af8fcbe17f2c3","tid":352700,"uid":5064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:39:25.000Z","msg":"做Partyroom同做餐廳一樣，見撚盡人生百態，你地有咩想問，我即管試吓答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c29d733426f21856df63ede0e999a8e92cff89","tid":352700,"uid":65390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:40:45.000Z","msg":"partyroom唔係租個場俾人就行開<br />\n完場先返黎執野咩？<br />\n點會做餐廳咁？"},{"pid":"0a1495d8ffb9263c1895cb40c8cf737269db50c7","tid":352700,"uid":5064,"like":1,"dislike":52,"score":-51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:43:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>partyroom唔係租個場俾人就行開<br />\n完場先返黎執野咩？<br />\n點會做餐廳咁？</blockquote><br />\n我果一間唔係，我係要係埋個場入面睇住啲人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc88245b28b3f7f6ae25af9ceda96c9c193e3e5","tid":352700,"uid":49163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:44:32.000Z","msg":"有咩牌要拎？"},{"pid":"c466cd97d8c63965dc9561516a983eb57e30dc00","tid":352700,"uid":62911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:46:33.000Z","msg":"做得開唔開心，有無遇過好麻煩既客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9e76e19dd0711f4392c0b2cf28f44d67e272cf","tid":352700,"uid":117237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:47:13.000Z","msg":"租黎拍咸片都幾好"},{"pid":"4b6fb89126e27a9c2ac6475c1dc3327c53901756","tid":352700,"uid":65390,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:47:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>partyroom唔係租個場俾人就行開<br />\n完場先返黎執野咩？<br />\n點會做餐廳咁？</blockquote><br />\n我果一間唔係，我係要係埋個場入面睇住啲人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打工？<br />\n咁不如正正經經搵份樓面做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432e8080596d3e81ea11d40cb39b06b52d9cb182","tid":352700,"uid":5064,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:52:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩牌要拎？</blockquote><br />\n呢層真係唔太知，我只係做前線service<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e656f9dd825e9cac1367c39b7d09a115f4ab7e","tid":352700,"uid":16878,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:53:55.000Z","msg":"仲有無我賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e83b97576e34deeddc8a2c14148bb75eddd1d60f","tid":352700,"uid":41520,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:54:25.000Z","msg":"有冇人當partyroom係炮房?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e359baa10d963ff3007f84202f545ae8e3f7ec0","tid":352700,"uid":25099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:54:42.000Z","msg":"幾樣野想問<br />\n1. 整爛你地啲野會唔會堅決要個客賠, 個客賴皮你地點做<br />\n2. overrun 賴死唔走你點趕走佢地<br />\n3. 試過啲客有幾冇手尾/ 幾污糟"},{"pid":"6a19d11899937146c17288c13dbab9d8ab1de9df","tid":352700,"uid":5064,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:57:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做得開唔開心，有無遇過好麻煩既客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有呀，好撚柒多，可以體驗到香港投訴之都既威力"},{"pid":"c853d4b630753d9a861661b975ca0986188aba19","tid":352700,"uid":5064,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:59:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>租黎拍咸片都幾好</blockquote><br />\n拍戲拍劇都有試過既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過有客試過係廁所扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be35173f4590768967d565c3a59144dfb12bb1f","tid":352700,"uid":5064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:03:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>partyroom唔係租個場俾人就行開<br />\n完場先返黎執野咩？<br />\n點會做餐廳咁？</blockquote><br />\n我果一間唔係，我係要係埋個場入面睇住啲人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打工？<br />\n咁不如正正經經搵份樓面做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁又唔同既，我呢份都算係輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時候有啲麻煩客啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31571dc8fdc036049b2d6dbd819f7dc76463139c","tid":352700,"uid":9577,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:10:52.000Z","msg":"有冇客搵埋你一齊玩, 然後做左朋友?"},{"pid":"105b4f2e3196e791418240b2eb04e3fe524959cf","tid":352700,"uid":118772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:20:10.000Z","msg":"做過一日 執房執到狗咁 人工雞碎咁多 試左一日即刻話唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba23e732140f32b90891c6a890fb876d92e08c03","tid":352700,"uid":18894,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:28:40.000Z","msg":"覺得party room抵唔抵玩?<br />\n搵party room有咩要注意?"},{"pid":"d3f123937801ee61a46f668dbec6882d64747848","tid":352700,"uid":73907,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:38:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>租黎拍咸片都幾好</blockquote><br />\n拍戲拍劇都有試過既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過有客試過係廁所扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n磨牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b828a11393c89acc834eef9b164a0940e9ba37d","tid":352700,"uid":5064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:01:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有無我賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有架"},{"pid":"6039e95e62f5fc36727642148d13108c0b593d57","tid":352700,"uid":5064,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:02:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇客搵埋你一齊玩, 然後做左朋友?</blockquote><br />\n都有既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 公司叫我地多啲同客玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf15aff8d6145f6b4f67e2a96d3eb1221235e60","tid":352700,"uid":5064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:03:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做過一日 執房執到狗咁 人工雞碎咁多 試左一日即刻話唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我果間係一個大場，冇間房，但都係執到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa4e30078624b983d73989512056e245671d24ed","tid":352700,"uid":65872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:06:18.000Z","msg":"工作時間彈唔彈性？<br />\n我都想搵份pt返下"},{"pid":"81acf415bdc120bc93d41a40e666126fd95ba422","tid":352700,"uid":5064,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:07:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾樣野想問<br />\n1. 整爛你地啲野會唔會堅決要個客賠, 個客賴皮你地點做<br />\n2. overrun 賴死唔走你點趕走佢地<br />\n3. 試過啲客有幾冇手尾/ 幾污糟</blockquote><br />\n1.一定會叫客人賠，好彩未試過遇到客賴皮<br />\n2.我就會熄冷氣再熄音樂，如果都係唔走先會報驚<br />\n3.嘩，問得好呀！試過全場地下濕晒，全部都係酒、汽水，好撚痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 清撚左我三個鐘"},{"pid":"91fabc128976493f8a93df30935eaa03f7315b10","tid":352700,"uid":5064,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:13:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得party room抵唔抵玩?<br />\n搵party room有咩要注意?</blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得大家搵party room都係想搵一個地方俾大家敘吓舊，有時候個重點都唔係價錢，不過我呢個場叫做多啲野玩，都算抵既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搵partyroom既話我個人好注重係環境，我去過其他partyroom，環境都唔算係好乾淨，而且有啲設施仲要壞左，加上個廁所都好污糟，所以我都好彩做到一間注重衛生既partyroom<br />\n<br />\n不過都要講句，我果間既收費都有啲貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e22b63dd3e75e5c402da6d060581a62fb6a6fe","tid":352700,"uid":20032,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:13:08.000Z","msg":"有無cam，有次想同女友係入面做愛"},{"pid":"d166633910f628d69ed92549d3877b78af71dd32","tid":352700,"uid":71257,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:14:19.000Z","msg":"D女玩起上黎會唔會走哂光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ce1b5957856d64177c815442102d413c826856","tid":352700,"uid":5064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:15:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>工作時間彈唔彈性？<br />\n我都想搵份pt返下</blockquote><br />\n都算有彈性架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾左更通常都有得番，試過做fyp成個月冇俾更都冇俾人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"758b0e847a2f74ec1de788028a87f4138b7c22c6","tid":352700,"uid":5064,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:17:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無cam，有次想同女友係入面做愛</blockquote><br />\n其他地方就有，廁所肯定冇，可以放心去廁所做"},{"pid":"735885a797d2da85802debee7a419105ed8f4857","tid":352700,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:18:05.000Z","msg":"其實多唔多人租，同咩人玩多　"},{"pid":"21afe4f7c6b33bbc5033fb76319076b9b9ec0dfd","tid":352700,"uid":48901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:18:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有咩牌要拎？</blockquote><br />\n呢層真係唔太知，我只係做前線service<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n商業登記業務性質果欄填咩？🤔"},{"pid":"255023d0fbd9e8ecb45192e5035c9c6f6c2a4b21","tid":352700,"uid":5064,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:18:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D女玩起上黎會唔會走哂光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有好多時都大開眼界，所以大家小心啲玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d2d0659c695b009860f47447d9749d18f79446c","tid":352700,"uid":5064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:20:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實多唔多人租，同咩人玩多　</blockquote><br />\n都多既，每日都有客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n男女老幼，黑白黃皮膚都見過"},{"pid":"fc746dcfa86420c20ebc71a234c04510964866f0","tid":352700,"uid":5455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:20:52.000Z","msg":"有冇西客on9投訴既例子"},{"pid":"aba5da99ace8c99ec08346351c1b8b270953bda2","tid":352700,"uid":55325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:22:52.000Z","msg":"小弟以前都係做party room<br />\n好坦白做呢行睇你識唔識玩<br />\n識玩既溝到女無問題啦<br />\n但如果你西口西面既就無咩計<br />\n利申做左年半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同樓主一樣"},{"pid":"cf87f64702497413b267f5f39a46717d0b79e2e3","tid":352700,"uid":5064,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:22:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>租黎拍咸片都幾好</blockquote><br />\n拍戲拍劇都有試過既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過有客試過係廁所扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n磨牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果陣坐緊reception 位見到有一男一女（後生既）拖住手入廁所，之後隔左半個鐘先出黎，出黎果陣仲係度整理自己衣領，之後班客走晒，去清垃圾桶果陣見到有用過既condom係地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d230ab0219f5470a41203002367ecf502c5c983","tid":352700,"uid":96402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:28:42.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講邊區"},{"pid":"cb8d720d991425b582bd26d4740a34eb92f00ae1","tid":352700,"uid":58448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:28:47.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣？"},{"pid":"7b181300e3738308a631e52c2e870c27d7e08bb4","tid":352700,"uid":10968,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:31:43.000Z","msg":"點睇好似我呢啲夠鐘會幫手執好個場既客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3202f0570b65c0c67ab68bf803ffd2e58a410958","tid":352700,"uid":5064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:34:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有咩牌要拎？</blockquote><br />\n呢層真係唔太知，我只係做前線service<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n商業登記業務性質果欄填咩？🤔</blockquote><br />\n真係唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923763ed13065f1d10be006fc77f3483d0c54096","tid":352700,"uid":2035,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:34:57.000Z","msg":"仲請唔請人？"},{"pid":"94a0ba06c2c909a938881f7339bbabfe7e22a323","tid":352700,"uid":55325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:37:36.000Z","msg":"無好既老闆真係狗也不屌呢行"},{"pid":"69ebf2cb7f3191e6a39b28